item.title: Mens 1st display a rapier wit
item.description: Like the Women’s team, the Men’s 1st Team Fencing also spent the weekend fencing in Hampstead Heath. Our league consisted of Oxford 1s, Cambridge 1s, UCL 1s, Bristol 1s, and us. Our first match of the weekend was against UCL, a match we needed to win if we were to avoid being in the relegation spot. …
